What is in reset: Heights in some browsers

How to make flid image?
css img{ max-width: 100% }

img,embed, object, video {
  max-width: 100%;
}

.feature {
  overflow: hidden;
}

.feature img {
  display: block;
  max-width: auto;
}

hint: use following to image responsive
img {
  max-width: 92%;
  margin: 4%;
}

img.hero {
  max-width: 100%;
  margin: 0;
}

